ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
SubjectTransfer of up to $500,000 from the CWB separate account to establish a Canadian Grain Policy Chair at the University of Saskatchewan
PrecisOrder authorizing the payment by the CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD of up to $500,000 from the separate account to establish and fund a Canadian Grain Policy Chair in the Department of Bioresource Policy, Business and Economics, College of Agriculture and Bioresources, at the University of Saskatchewan.
